{"aid": "http://arxiv.org/abs/2504.11030v1", "title": "Sobolev homeomorphisms and composition operators on homogeneous Lie
  groups", "summary": "In this article we study Sobolev homeomorphisms and composition operators on
homogeneous Lie groups. We prove, that a measurable homeomorphism $\varphi:
\Omega \to\widetilde{\Omega}$ belongs to the Sobolev space $L^{1}_{q}(\Omega;
\widetilde{\Omega})$, $1\leq q < \infty$, if and only if $\varphi$ generates a
bounded composition operator on Sobolev spaces.", "main_category": "math.AP", "categories": "math.AP", "published": "2025-04-15T09:53:36Z"}
